page.title: 11About Me: by Mastaf
page.content: My name is{Mastaf,}I am an eleven year old{Bengali}boy with short, dark hair and brown eyes,I go to Greenfield primary school. I have four brothers Mostab, Mastak, Mustar and baby Mahmud. My sister lives in Bangladesh, she is married with two children,her husband is a doctor. I like football, I support Manchester United, my favourite player is Brian Robson; I also like reading. I go to the{mosque}to read all about muslems and I go to a local Bengali Youth Club to play pool and table tennis. I have my supper at 8 o'clock and go to bed at 10 o'clock. In the morning I wake up at 7 and have my breakfast before coming to school about five minutes to nine. I have school dinners my favourite meal is curried fish.
